node.text:
The highlight of 2020 for me was launching a business that marries my passion for medicine and beauty all rolled into one. That’s why I’m happy to announce that my brand @muze.labs will now be available at @musclelab. If you drop by the facility to workout or rehab, make sure to grab some wipes💧

It was important to find a brand that aligns with our mission to promote a healthy lifestyle for all people. Whether it’s skin care or fitness, it’s all about self care. Make this upcoming year about bettering yourself in all aspects. Muze does it all, because you do it all 🦾

node.text:
— Happy Sunday! We out ladies and gentlemen ✈️ I’ve been working long and hard to bring to you a fun, exotic, once in a lifetime trip experience with me. Get your passports ready and let's go! 😍 

I've partnered with @onelovetravel.club to put together a 4-day content trip to Punta Cana, Dominican Republic. 🌴🇩🇴 This will be my first trip to DR, so we get to enjoy it together! Sign up NOW before we meet the max number of people!

We'll spend 4-days together capturing amazing content of course and while exploring DR with adventure activities like riding ATVs and chilling on a catamaran. ⚠️ Don’t forget to get your special DR. ROBIN B VIP EXCLUSIVE EXPERIENCE WITH ME by selecting “VIP UPGRADE” 🔝❤️ I can't wait to meet you guys! 

Head to http://onelovetravel.club/punta-cana-november-2021 to register. 

#Dr.RobinhitsDRwiththecrew
#OneLoveTakesDR #traveldoc #drrobinb

node.text:
— Excuse the language, but this week I SECURED the bag! Yes, all in a week’s work 😅 Celebrate yourself by saying when you did a “GOOD JOB” ‼️

They say you need 5 hobbies:

1️⃣ One to make you money.
2️⃣ One to keep you in shape.
3️⃣ One to keep you creative.
4️⃣ One to build knowledge.
5️⃣ One to evolve your mindset.

Remember — it’s never to late to re-invent yourself. You’re never too old to learn new tricks. It just takes the desire to grow in every aspect. Financially, mentally, physically, and spiritually.

Don’t forget how important networking and building relationships are too! Relationships are social currency 🤞🏽
